Results from 4 studies were not included in the meta-analysis. Naguib 2001 and Mellis 2006 did not report sufficient data to estimate effects. Estimated standard errors from ranges reported in Yagmudrur 2011 were exceedingly small yielding an outlier effect. Reported IQR from Zhang 2019 carbohydrate arm did not allow variance estimation.
